{"tid":903694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京毒霧來襲 司機看不到紅綠燈","createTime":"2018-11-15T18:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T13:53:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":163,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"38eda6dec282813b07c1c3de443911fef218625d","tid":903694,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/capturesmog.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fcapturesmog.png&h=ad40180c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國北方毒霧捲土重來，北京民眾今早14日被濃重的毒霧罩住。北京街上一度無法辨識紅綠燈。氣象部門發布黃色大霧警報。<br />\n<br />\n今天中國網絡流傳一段視頻顯示，街頭一人向若隱若現的交警喊話：&ldquo;警察叔叔，現在紅燈綠燈啊？等半天了，看不見！&rdquo;。有報道稱，今天北京部分地區能見度不到200米。<br />\n<br />\n預測今天下午至明天上午，北京污染程度將會加劇。北京居民被呼籲最好不要出門，環保監測中心建議人們採取防護措施。這是今年入冬以來，北京最嚴重空氣污染。北京全市35個監測站點中17個站點達到重度污染，13個站點顯示嚴重污染。部分地區空氣中PM2.5濃度，每立方米超過300微克。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20181114-北京霧霾來襲-司機看不到紅綠燈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20181114-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%9C%A7%E9%9C%BE%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E7%B4%85%E7%B6%A0%E7%87%88&d=w6KT%2BKEW50acgijZ%2FDEmhcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0c0a6bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20181114-北京霧霾來襲-司機看不到紅綠燈</a>"},{"pid":"bbce4c08de53f8addbda2f8d11ba4d92aef92220","tid":903694,"uid":199162,"like":415,"dislike":3,"score":412,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:05:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲傻閪國家簡直係史書上嘅笑話"},{"pid":"889657faf31451be32343ddd48053cb5e8147a6a","tid":903694,"uid":65858,"like":126,"dislike":1,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"7de6790fd37953dbc84d00c74fb9c83484b7dd77","tid":903694,"uid":137921,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"ci